  "statement": "The discovery program consists of two coupled models: an operational subsystem model for runtime_environment, codex_local_agent, codex_cloud_worker, and orchestration_daemon, and an epistemic/control/governance model that tracks evidence, accepted relationships, accepted identity, applied control, and fidelity review about that operational system.",
